	edges.  Must fit into region called Faerie.  All forest locs.
	But no harvesting allowed.  Or enchanted forest locs.

	Instead of wrapping edges, line with water locations.  Mwah ha ha.
	They can't make ships in Faerie.  Ha ha ha!

    3.	Seed with a Faerie hill in each location.

    4.  Faerie hills exist both in Faerie as well as somewhere in the
        real world, from time to time.  Faerie stone can summon them.
	(Once a year they appear).

    5.  Faerie cities sell rare, nifty things.

    6.  Faerie has the Elven Hunt who attacks anyone they see, except
	those who possess a faerie stone.

    7.  No building in Faerie.

    8.  Save faerie region in system file.  If region(where) == reg_faerie
		if (in_faerie(where/who))


