Spirit World
------------

New magical skill category allows one's spirit to leave the body
and travel in the spirit world.

	o  use to cause spirit to appear next to body (stacked with?)

	o  use to capture a demon

	o  links from all graveyards to Hades

	o  Hades is maze-like, with various demons about




	-  Harmful to the body -- incurs health loss

	-  Spirit is a separate entity one may give special orders to.

		RETURN causes the spirit to cease existing, and returns
		control to the living body.

		The noble is inactive while the spirit exists.

	-  Spirit-on-death bit.  When one dies, one becomes a spirit
	   in Hades.

	-  Spirits can't pick up things

	-  Spirits only know spirit magic that they took with them.
	   If they learn more in the spirit realm, they bring the
	   knowledge back with them.


